    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [b].[Id] AS [Id0], [b].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [b].[Image], [b].[Name] AS [Name0], [c].[Id] AS [Id1], [c].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [c].[Image] AS [Image0], [c].[Name] AS [Name1]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1]

    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]

    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [b].[Id] AS [Id0], [b].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [b].[Image], [b].[Name] AS [Name0], [c].[Id] AS [Id1], [c].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [c].[Image] AS [Image0], [c].[Name] AS [Name1]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[ColorId], [p0].[CreateDate], [p0].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p0].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[TagId], [t2].[Id] AS [Id0], [t2].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [t2].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t2] ON [p1].[TagId] = [t2].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p2] ON [t].[Id] = [p2].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductComments] AS [p3] ON [t].[Id] = [p3].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [p2].[Id]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AppUserId], [o].[CreateDate], [o].[StripeId], [o].[TotalPrice], [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[FullName], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[OrderId], [t].[Price], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Quantity], [t].[Id0], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreateDate0], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t].[Price0]
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [o].[AppUserId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[Price], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [o].[Id] = [t].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [t].[Id]

FROM [Orders] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [o].[AppUserId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[Price], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0]

) AS [t] ON [o].[Id] = [t].[OrderId]

    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [b].[Id] AS [Id0], [b].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [b].[Image], [b].[Name] AS [Name0], [c].[Id] AS [Id1], [c].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [c].[Image] AS [Image0], [c].[Name] AS [Name1]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[ColorId], [p0].[CreateDate], [p0].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [c0].[Name]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [b].[Id] AS [Id0], [b].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [b].[Image], [b].[Name] AS [Name0], [c].[Id] AS [Id1], [c].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [c].[Image] AS [Image0], [c].[Name] AS [Name1]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[ColorId], [p0].[CreateDate], [p0].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p0].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[TagId], [t2].[Id] AS [Id0], [t2].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [t2].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t2] ON [p1].[TagId] = [t2].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p2] ON [t].[Id] = [p2].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductComments] AS [p3] ON [t].[Id] = [p3].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [p2].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [b].[Id] AS [Id0], [b].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [b].[Image], [b].[Name] AS [Name0], [c].[Id] AS [Id1], [c].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [c].[Image] AS [Image0], [c].[Name] AS [Name1]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1]

    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[ColorId], [p0].[CreateDate], [p0].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p0].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[TagId], [t2].[Id] AS [Id0], [t2].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [t2].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t2] ON [p1].[TagId] = [t2].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p2] ON [t].[Id] = [p2].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductComments] AS [p3] ON [t].[Id] = [p3].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [p2].[Id]
